msgid "View and organize your images"
msgstr "查看及管理图像"

#. Translators: Search terms to find this application. Do NOT translate or localize the semicolons. The list MUST also end with a semicolon.
#: data/app.gthumb.gthumb-devel.desktop.in:5
#: data/app.gthumb.gthumb.desktop.in:5
msgid "Image;Viewer;"
msgstr "Image;Viewer;图像;浏览器;查看;照片;"

#: data/app.gthumb.gthumb-devel.desktop.in:17
#: data/app.gthumb.gthumb.desktop.in:17 src/Ext/Shortcuts/Shortcuts.vala:133
msgid "New Window"
msgstr "新建窗口"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:20
msgid "Image viewer, editor, browser and organizer."
msgstr "图像查看工具、编辑工具、浏览器和整理工具。"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:23
msgid "View images: PNG, JPEG, WEBP, SVG, JXL, HEIF, AVIF, TIFF, GIF, RAW."
msgstr "查看图像：PNG, JPEG, WEBP, SVG, JXL, HEIF, AVIF, TIFF, GIF, RAW。"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:26
msgid ""
"Edit images: scale, rotate and crop images, change contrast, brightness and "
"saturation, as well as other color transformations."
msgstr ""
"编辑图像：缩放、旋转以及裁剪图像，调整色彩饱和度，亮度，对比度以及其他颜色变"
"换。"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:29
msgid "View and edit embedded metadata: EXIF, IPTC and XMP."
msgstr "查看和编辑嵌入的元数据：EXIF, IPTC 和 XMP。"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:32
msgid ""
"File manager operations: copy, move, rename and delete files and folders, "
"execute scripts on the selected files."
msgstr ""
"文件管理器操作：复制、移动、重命名和删除文件与文件夹、对选中的文件执行脚本。"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:35
msgid "Image specific tools:"
msgstr "图像专用工具："

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:39
msgid "JPEG lossless transformations"
msgstr "JPEG 无损变换"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:40
msgid "Image resize"
msgstr "图像缩放"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:41
msgid "Format conversion"
msgstr "格式转换"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:42
msgid "Slideshow"
msgstr "幻灯片放映"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:43
msgid "Setting an image as desktop background"
msgstr "将图像设置为桌面背景"

#: data/appdata/app.gthumb.gthumb.metainfo.xml.in:45
msgid ""
"Add comments and other metadata to images, organize images in catalogs and "
"catalogs in libraries, search for images and save the result as a catalog."
msgstr ""
"添加评论以及其他元数据至图像，管理一览表中的图像以及图库中的一览表，搜索图像"
"以及另存搜索结果为一览表。"

